title: Clinton Testifies on Benghazi, and All Seats Are Hot Ones
text: The two big open questions that have been hanging over Washington for weeks seem to be resolved as Vice President Joseph R. Biden Jr. announced that he would not seek the presidency, and Representative Paul D. Ryan of Wisconsin received the pledge of unity that could clear his path toward becoming speaker of the House. ...
